# PastoralProtect — environment templates (monorepo)
#
# There is no single root .env loaded by the apps. Copy each template into the
# matching path (never commit real .env files — see .gitignore).
#
#   backend/.env.example          →  backend/.env
#   frontend/.env.example         →  frontend/.env.local
#   contracts/.env.example        →  contracts/.env          (optional Hardhat)
#   storacha-uploader/.env.example → storacha-uploader/.env (optional IPFS bridge)
#
# Full checklist: docs/SETUP.md
